<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_542_r2l20"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>vyhperg<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns nehſt <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıng<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_542_r2l21">der <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu velden . wıe ein padknecht <expan>genan<ex>n</ex>t</expan> hanns . der yecʒ bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_542_r2l22">vns <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . als Jr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> hett . der <expan>rechtſchuldıg<ex>en</ex></expan> einr ſölt ſein etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_542_r2l23">haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vorſch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_542_r2l24">darnach gehabt haben / vnd ıſt vns geſagt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> Hanns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_542_r2l25">padknecht dennoch <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>nehſtu<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> mıtwochen bey vns <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_542_r2l26">vnd <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> abends awſʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat <expan>gecʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd yecʒ <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒulawff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_542_r2l27">ſüll ſein . das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch daʒ Jr eẅch darnach wıſſet ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_542_r2l28">rıchten. Vnd wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
