</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_542" id="270r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Vyhperg<ex>er</ex></expan>, vogt zu Herspruk </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Vyhperg<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns nehst
                            <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ding<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie der
                            <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Velden, wie ein padknecht
                                <expan>genan<ex>n</ex>t</expan> Hanns, der yecz bey uns
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, als ir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> hett, der
                                <expan>rechtschuldig<ex>en</ex></expan> einr sölt sein etc., das
                        haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> vorsch darnach gehabt haben; und ist uns
                        gesagt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
                        Hanns padknecht dennoch <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                mitwochen</q>21./28.10./04./11./18.11.1422</note>
</app> bey uns <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> abends awsz
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat <expan>geczog<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                        yecz <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> zu Lawff süll sein. Das
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch, daz ir ewch
                        darnach wisset zu richten. Und wo wir ewch lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
